‚∏ª

US1 ‚Äî Select activity on tablet (Survey or Signature)

As a visitor
I want to choose between giving feedback or signing a form
So that I can start the correct process on the tablet

Description

When arriving on the tablet, the visitor sees a welcome screen with:
	‚Ä¢	Two main actions:
	‚Ä¢	Opinion Survey
	‚Ä¢	eSignature
	‚Ä¢	Each action is represented by a large, clearly identifiable button.

Only the eSignature path is in scope for this epic.

Acceptance Criteria

GIVEN I am on the tablet welcome screen
THEN I see two main actions: Opinion Survey and eSignature

WHEN I click on eSignature
THEN I am redirected to the signature code entry screen


‚∏ª

US2 ‚Äî Enter validation code on tablet

As a visitor
I want to enter the validation code given by the coach
So that I can access my return summary

Description

After selecting eSignature, the visitor sees:
	‚Ä¢	An instruction explaining that a code was provided by the coach
	‚Ä¢	A virtual keyboard
	‚Ä¢	A code input field (2 characters)
	‚Ä¢	A validation action via the green confirmation key

Acceptance Criteria

GIVEN I am on the code entry screen
THEN a virtual keyboard is displayed
AND a code input field is visible

WHEN I enter a 2-character code and press the validation key
THEN the code is submitted

WHEN the code is invalid
THEN an error message is displayed
AND I remain on the code entry screen


