THEN the return summary screen is displayed

AND the summary is read-only

WHEN I click on Confirm and Sign
THEN I am redirected to the signature screen


‚∏ª

US4 ‚Äî Capture signature on tablet

As a visitor
I want to sign the form using my finger
So that I can officially confirm the return

